INSERT INTO `grammar` VALUES (1,NULL,NULL,'2022-04-20 15:31:14.735000','admin','<p><h2>1. Cch dng</h2></p>  <p>Th hin ti n c s dng trong cc trng hp sau:</p><p></p><p>Dng  din t thi quen hoc nhng vic thng xuyn xy ra  hin ti</p><p>V d: We go to school every day.  (Ti i hc mi ngy) </p><p></p><p>Dng  din t nhng s vt, s vic xy ra mang tnh quy lut</p><p>V d:  This festival occur every 3 years. (L hi ny din ra 3 nm mt ln.)</p><p></p><p>Dng  din t cc s tht hin nhin, mt chn l, cc phong tc tp qun, cc hin tng t nhin.</p><p>V d: The earth moves around the Sun. (Tri t quay quanh mt tri)</p><p></p><p>Dng  din t lch trnh ca tu, xe, my bay,</p><p>V d: The train leaves at 8 am tomorrow. (Tu khi hnh lc 8 gi sng mai.)</p><p></p><p><h2>2. Cu trc</h2></p><p>Mt s cu trc ca th hin ti n cn ghi nh:</p><p></p><p><b>ng t thng: </b></p><p>(+) Khng nh: S + V (s,es) + O</p><p></p><p>(-) Ph nh: S + don\'t/doesn\'t + V + O</p><p></p><p>(?) Cu hi: Do/Does + S + V + O?</p><p></p><p>         Wh - question + Do/Does + S + V + O?</p><p></p><p><b>ng t Tobe: </b></p><p>(+) Khng nh: S + is/are/am + Adj/Adv/N</p><p></p><p>(-) Ph nh: S + isn\'t/aren\'t/amn\'t + Adj/Adv/N</p><p></p><p>(?) Cu hi: Is/are/am + S + Adj/Adv/N?</p><p></p><p>                 Wh-question + Is/are/am + S?</p><p></p><p>Gii thch k hiu: Xem chi tit</p><p></p><p><b>Lu : </b></p><p>Tr ng t \"Do\" s i vi cc ch ng s nhiu: I, you, we, they....</p><p>Tr ng t \"Does\" s i vi cc ch ng s t: He, She, It, Tn ring...</p><p>ng t tobe \"Am\" s i vi ch ng: I</p><p>ng t tobe \"Are\" s i vi ch ng s nhiu: You, we, they...</p><p>ng t  tobe \"Is\" s i vi ch ng s t: She, he, it, tn ring...</p><p>ng t thng V khi i vi ch ng s nhiu (I, you, we, they...) th gi nguyn th</p><p>ex: I go to school</p><p></p><p>ng t thng V khi i vi ch ng s t (She, he, it, tn ring...) th thm \"s/es\"</p><p>V d: She goes to school/He eats cake</p><p></p><p><h2>3. Cch nhn bit</h2></p><p>Khi trong cu c xut hin cc ph t sau, th cc bn s vn dng cu trc ca th hin ti n:</p><p></p><p>Always (lun lun) , usually (thng xuyn), often (thng xuyn), frequently (thng xuyn) , sometimes (thnh thong), seldom (him khi), rarely (him khi), hardly (him khi) , never (khng bao gi), generally (nhn chung), regularly (thng xuyn).</p><p>Every day, every week, every month, every year,. (Mi ngy, mi tun, mi thng, mi nm)</p><p>Once/ twice/ three times/ four times.. a day/ week/ month/ year,. (mt ln / hai ln/ ba ln/ bn ln ..mt ngy/ tun/ thng/ nm)</p><p><h2>4. BI TP V HNG DN GII</h2></p><p><b>Bi 1: in tr ng t: </b></p><p></p><p>I don\'t. like milk.</p><p>She . play volleyball in the afternoon.</p><p>He . go to bed at midnight.</p><p>They.do the homework on weekends.</p><p>The bus .arrive at 8.30 a.m</p><p><b>Bi 2: Chn dng ng ca t</b></p><p></p><p>He catch/catches robbers.</p><p>My mother is a driver. She always wear/wears a white coat.</p><p>They never drink/drinks beer.</p><p>Michel go/goes window shopping seven times a month.</p><p>She have/has a book.</p><p> <b>Bi 3: Vit li cu hon chnh</b></p><p></p><p>Eg: They / wear suits to work? =>Do they wear suits to work?</p><p></p><p>I / not / sleep late at the weekends =>________</p><p>we / not / believe the Prime Minister =>________</p><p>you / understand the question? =>________</p><p>they / not / work late on Thusday  =>________</p><p>Your friends / want some coffee? =>________</p><p><b> Bi 4: in dng ng ca t trong ngoc</b></p><p></p><p>he (not study) . on Sunday.</p><p>she (have) . a new T-shirt today.</p><p>I usually (have) .breakfast at 6.00 a.m.</p><p>Peter (not/ study).very hard. He never gets high scores.</p><p>My mother often (teach).me English on Saturday.</p>','PRESENT-SIMPLE-1-1.jpg','present_simple.png','Th hin ti n Present Simple','Bi vit ny s cung cp cho cc bn ton b kin thc l thuyt lin quan n th hin ti n. V c nhng bi tp vn dng  gip cc bn d ghi nh, d thuc, t im s cao hn trong cc bi kim tra.'),(2,NULL,NULL,'2022-04-20 15:35:10.632000','admin','<p><h2>1. Cu trc</h2></p><p>Mt s cu trc c s dng trong th hin ti tip din:</p><p></p><p>(+) Khng nh: S + am/ is/ are + V-ing</p><p></p><p>(-) Ph nh: S + am/ is/ are + not + V-ing</p><p></p><p>(?) Cu hi yes/no: Am/ Is/ Are + S + V-ing   ?</p><p></p><p>- Yes, I + am</p><p></p><p>- Yes, he/ she/ it + is.</p><p></p><p>-Yes, we/ you/ they + are</p><p></p><p>- No, I + am not</p><p></p><p>- No, he/ she/ it + isnt</p><p></p><p>- No, we/ you/ they + arent.</p><p></p><p>(?) Cu hi Wh - question: Wh - question + Is/are/am + S + V-ing?</p><p></p><p>Gii thch k hiu: Xem chi tit</p><p></p><p><b>Lu </b></p><p>ng t tobe \"Am\" s i vi ch ng: I</p><p>ng t tobe \"Are\" s i vi ch ng s nhiu: You, we, they...</p><p>ng t  tobe \"Is\" s i vi ch ng s t: She, he, it, tn ring...</p><p>Khi ph nh: Isn\'t, Aren\'t, Am not</p><p>Quy tc thm ing sau ng t: Thng thng ta ch cn cng thm -ing vo sau ng t.</p><p>Nhng c mt s ch :</p><p></p><p>Vi ng t tn cng l MT ch e: Ta b e ri thm -ing.</p><p></p><p>Vi ng t c MT m tit, tn cng l MT PH M, trc l MT NGUYN M: Ta nhn i ph m cui ri thm -ing.</p><p></p><p></p><p> </p><p>Vi ng t tn cng l ie: Ta i ie thnh y ri thm -ing.</p><p></p><p><h2>2. Cch dng</h2></p><p>Th hin ti tip din c s dng trong cc trng hp sau:</p><p></p><p>Din t mt hnh ng ang xy ra ngay ti thi im ni.</p><p>V d: I am looking for a new job. (Ti ang tm kim mt cng vic mi.) Ta hiu t ngay ti lc ni ngi ni ang khng i np h s hay  tm vic m trong thi gian  (c th bt u trc  c thng) ngi ni ang tm kim mt cng vic. Nhng khi mun ni chung chung rng iu g ang xy ra xung quanh thi im  ta cng s dng th hin ti tip din.</p><p></p><p>Din t mt s vic s xy ra trong tng lai theo mt k hoch  c ln lch c nh.</p><p>V d: I bought the ticket yesterday. I am flying to New York tomorrow. Ta thy c cn c, k hoch r rng (ti  mua v my bay) nn ta s dng th hin ti tip din  ni v mt vic chc chn s xy ra trong tng lai.</p><p></p><p>Din t mt hnh ng ang xy ra ngay ti thi im ni.</p><p>V d: We are studying Maths now. (By gi chng ti ang hc ton) Ta thy ti thi im ni (by gi) th vic hc ton ang din ra nn ta s dng th hin ti tip din  din t.</p><p></p><p>Din t s khng hi lng hay phn nn v vic g trong cu s dng always. </p><p>V d: She always goes to school at 6.30 am. (C y lun i hc vo lc 6h30). Nhng khi mun din t s kh chu hay mun phn nn v iu g ta s dng th hin ti tip din  ni.)</p><p></p><p><h2>3. Du hiu nhn bit</h2></p><p>Khi trong cu xut hin cc t sau, chng ta chia  th hin ti tip din:</p><p></p><p>Trong cu c cc trng t ch thi gian:</p><p> Now: by gi, Right now: Ngay by gi, At the moment: lc ny, At present: hin ti, At + gi c th (at 12 olock)</p><p></p><p>Trong cu c cc ng t nh:</p><p>Look! (Nhn ka!) - Listen! (Hy nghe ny!) - Keep silent! (Hy im lng) V d: - Now my sister is going shopping with my mother. (By gi em gi ti ang i mua sm vi m ca ti.) - Look! The train is coming. (Nhn kia! tu ang n.) - Listen! Someone is crying. (Nghe ny! Ai  ang khc.) - Keep silent! The baby is sleeping. (Hy im lng! Em b ang ng.)</p><p><h2>4. Bi tp vn dng</h2></p><p><b>Bi 1: Vit li cu cho ng: </b></p><p></p><p>1. (she/ go to school now)</p><p></p><p>2. (I/ read a science book)</p><p></p><p>3. (she/ not/ wash her hand)</p><p></p><p>4. (the cat/ chase mice?)</p><p></p<p>5. (she/ cry?)</p><p></p><p>6. (he/ not/ study English)</p><p></p><p>7. (we/ drive to Ha Noi city?)</p><p></p><p>8. (they/ watch TV?)</p><p></p><p>9. (where/ she/ go now?)</p><p></p><p>10. (I/ not/ leave home now)</p><p></p><p><b>Bi 2: Chia ng t ng trong cc cu sau</b></p><p></p><p>1. It (get)....... dark. Shall I turn on the light?</p><p></p><p>2. They don\'t have any where to live at the moment. They(stay)...... with their uncle until they find somewhere.</p><p></p><p></p><p> </p><p>3. Why are all these people here? What (happen)..........?</p><p></p><p>4. Where is your mother? She........ (watch) TV in the living room.</p><p></p><p>5. The student (not, learn)..... in class at present</p><p></p><p>6. Some people (not drink)............ tea now.</p><p></p><p>7. At present, he (compose)............ a piece of music for his wife</p><p></p><p>8. We (have)............. dinner in a beautiful resataurant right now</p><p></p><p>9.  Keep silent! You (talk) ............. so loudly.</p><p></p><p>10. Look! The car (go) .....  so fast.</p><p></p><p><b>Bi 3: Vit li cu vi cc gi  sau</b></p><p></p><p>1. My/ father/ water/ some plants/ the/ garden.</p><p></p><p>2. My/ mother/ clean/ floor/.</p><p></p><p>3. Mary/ have/ lunch/ her/ friends/ a/ restaurant.</p><p></p><p>4. They/ ask/ a/ man/ about/ the/ way/ the/ rainway/ station.</p><p></p><p>5. My/ student/ draw/ a/ beautiful/ picture</p>','7.1.jpg','Present Progressive.jpg','Th hin ti tip din Present Progressive','Bi vit ny s cung cp cho cc bn ton b kin thc l thuyt lin quan n th hin ti tip din. V c nhng bi tp vn dng  gip cc bn d ghi nh, d thuc, t im s cao hn trong cc bi kim tra.'),(3,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p><h2>1. Cu trc</h2></p><p>Vi th hin ti hon thnh, chng ta s s dng nhng cu trc sau:</p><p></p><p>(+) Khng nh: S + have/has + Vp2 + O</p><p></p><p>(-) Ph nh: S + haven\'t/ hasn\'t + Vp2 + O</p><p></p><p>(?) Cu hi yes/no: Have/has + S + Vp2 + O</p><p></p><p>Tr li: Yes, S + have/has, No + haven\'t/hasn\'t</p><p></p><p>(?) Cu hi Wh-question: Wh-question + have/has + S + Vp2</p><p></p><p>Gii thch k hiu: Xem chi tit</p><p></p><p><b>Lu </b></p><p> Vp2: ng t qu kh phn t (C quy tc  th thm ed sau V, Bt quy tc:  ct th 3 t tri sang trong bng ng t bt quy tc)</p><p></p><p>Tr ng t have i vi cc ch ng s nhiu: I, you, we, they...</p><p>Tr ng t has i vi cc ch ng s t: It, she, he, tn ring...</p><p>Phn bit tr ng t have/has vi ng t have (c)</p><p><h2>2. Cch dng</h2></p><p>Chng ta s dng th hin ti hon thnh trong cc trng hp sau:</p><p></p><p>Hnh ng  hon thnh cho ti thi im hin ti m khng  cp ti n xy ra khi no.</p><p>V d : Ive done all my homeworks / Ti  lm ht bi tp v nh</p><p></p><p>Hnh ng bt u  qu kh v ang tip tc  hin ti :</p><p>V d : She has lived in Liverpool all her life/ C y  sng c i  Liverpool.</p><p></p><p>Hnh ng  tng lm trc y v by gi vn cn lm</p><p>V d: He has written three books and he is working on another book/ Anh y  vit c 3 cun sch v ang vit cun tip theo</p><p></p><p>Mt kinh nghim cho ti thi im hin ti (thng dng trng t ever)</p><p>V d : My last birthday was the best day Ive ever had./ Sinh nht nm ngoi l ngy tuyt nht i ti.</p><p></p><p>V mt hnh ng trong qu kh nhng quan trng ti thi im ni</p><p>V d : I cant get my house. Ive lost my keys. /Ti khng th vo nh c. Ti nh mt chm cha kha ca mnh ri. </p><p></p><p><h2>3. Cch nhn bit</h2></p><p>Khi trong cu xut hin cc du hiu sau, ta chia  th hin ti hon thnh:</p><p></p><p>Just, recently, lately: gn y, va mi</p><p></p><p>already: ri</p><p></p><p>before: trc y</p><p></p><p>ever:  tng</p><p></p><p>never: cha tng, khng bao gi</p><p></p><p>for + N  qung thi gian: trong khong (for a year, for a long time, )</p><p></p><p>since + N  mc/im thi gian: t khi (since 1992, since June, )</p><p></p><p>yet: cha (dng trong cu ph nh v cu hi)</p><p></p><p>so far = until now = up to now = up to the present: cho n by gi</p><p></p><p><h2>4. Bi tp vn dng</h2></p><p><b>Bi 1: Chia cc ng t</b></p><p></p><p>I ( not work) today.</p><p>We (buy)..a new lamp.</p><p>We (not / plan)..our holiday yet.</p><p>Where (be / you) ?</p><p>He (write)..five letters.</p><p>She (not / see)..him for a long time.</p><p>(be / you)..at school?</p><p>School (not / start)..yet.</p><p>(speak / he)..to his boss?</p><p>No, he (have / not)..the time yet.</p><p><b>Bi 2: Vit li cu</b></p><p></p><p>I (work) very hard for this exam.</p><p>I (live) here since 1970.</p><p>You (be) to the zoo?</p><p>I\'m afraid you (look) at the wrong one.</p><p>Why are the police here? What (happen)!</p>','jAV4MCV5yyDc9v06.png','present-perfect.jpg','Th hin ti hon thnh Present Perfect','Bi vit ny s cung cp ton b kin thc l thuyt lin quan n th hin ti hon thnh. V c nhng bi tp vn dng  gip cc bn d ghi nh, d thuc, t im s cao hn trong cc bi kim tra.'),(4,NULL,NULL,'2022-04-20 15:36:23.913000','admin','<p><h2>1. Cch dng</h2></p> <p>Chng ta s s dng th qu kh n trong nhng trng hp sau:</p><p></p><p>Dng  din t mt hnh ng  xy ra v kt thc trong qu kh.</p><p>V d: They went to the concert last night. (H  ti rp ht ti hm qua.)</p><p></p><p>Din t mt s vic xy ra trong mt khong thi gian trong qu kh v  kt thc hon ton  hin ti</p><p>V d: When I was young, I often played soccer (Khi ti cn tr, ti thng chi  bng)</p><p></p<p> Din t mt lot hnh ng xy ra k tip nhau trong qu kh</p><p>V d: She came home, switched on the computer and checked information</p><p>(C y v nh, khi ng my tnh v kim tra hp th in t ca mnh)</p><p></p><p>Din t mt hnh ng chen ngang vo hnh ng khc ang xy ra trong qu kh (qu kh n dng kt hp vi qu kh tip din)</p><p>V d: When I was reading book, my dad called me (Khi ti ang c sch, b ti  gi)</p><p></p><p><h2>2. Cu trc</h2></p><p>Sau y l cu trc ca th qu kh n:</p><p></p><p><b>a. Vi ng t thng</b></p><p></p><p>(+) Khng nh: S + V-ed/P1 + O</p><p>(-) Ph nh: S + didn\'t + V + O</p><p>(?) Hi:</p><p>Wh-question + did + S + V?</p><p>Did + S + V...? Yes/No, S + did/didn\'t</p><p><b>b. Vi ng t tobe</b></p><p></p><p>(+) Khng nh: S + was/were + Adj/N</p><p>(-) Ph nh: S + wasn\'t/ weren\'t + Adj/N</p><p>(?) Hi:</p><p>Wh question + was/were + S?</p><p> Was/were + S + Adj/N?</p><p>Gii thch k hiu: Xem chi tit</p><p></p><p><b>c. Lu : </b></p><p></p><p>P1: ng t chia  th qu kh, ct th 2 trong bng ng t bt quy tc. Cn li thm -ed</p><p>ng t tobe \"was\" i vi cc ch ng s t: She,he, it, tn ring...</p><p>ng t tobe \"were\" i vi cc ch ng s nhiu : you, we, they...</p><p><h2>3. Du hiu nhn bit</h2></p><p>Khi trong cu xut hin cc du hiu sau, ta chia  th qu kh n:</p><p></p><p>Th qu kh n thng xut hin trong cu c nhng t sau y: yesterday, ago, finally, at last, in the last centyry, in the past, last(week, month, year), in (2013, June), in the (2000, 1970s), from (March) to (April), </p><p>Ngoi ra bn nn ch  n cc t ch thi gian qu kh khc v ng cnh ca cu ni.</p><p><h2>4. Bi tp vn dng</h2></p><p><b>Bi tp 1: Vit li cu</b></p><p></p><p>1. It/ be/ cloudy/ yesterday.</p><p></p><p>2. In 1990/ we/ move/ to another city.</p><p></p><p>3. When/ you/ get/ the first gift?</p><p></p><p>4.She/ not/ go/ to the church/ five days ago.</p><p></p><p>5. How/ be/ he/ yesterday?</p><p></p><p>6. and Mrs. James/ come back home/ and/ have/ lunch/ late/ last night?</p><p></p><p>7. They/ happy/ last holiday ?</p><p></p><p>8. How/ you/ get there?</p><p></p><p>9. I/ play/ football/ last/ Sunday.</p><p></p><p>10. My/ mother/ make/ two/ cake/ four/ day/ ago.</p><p></p><p><b>Bi tp 2: Chia dng ng ca t</b></p><p></p><p>       Snow White was the daughter of a beautiful queen, who died when the girl (be)1........... young. Her father (marry)2.............again, but the girls stepmother was very jealous of her because she was so beautiful. The evil queen (order)3.............a hunter to kill Snow White but he couldnt do it because she was so lovely. He (chase)4.............her away instead, and she (take)5.............refuge with seven dwarfs in their house in the forest. She (live)6.............with the dwarfs and took care of them and they (love)7.............her dearly. Then one day the talking mirror (tell)8.............the evil queen that Snow White was still alive. She (change)9.............herself into a witch and (make)10.............a poisoned apple. She (go)11.............to the dwarfs house disguised as an old woman and tempted Snow White to eat the poisoned apple, which (put)12.............her into an everlasting sleep. Finally, a prince (find)13.............her in the glass coffin where the dwarfs had put her and woke her up with a kiss. Snow White and the prince (be)14.............married and lived happily ever after.</p>','bGe4B8E1FP15rC6t.jpeg','grammar-games-thumbnail-past-simple-sentences.jpg','Th qu kh n Past simple','Bi vit cung cp cho bn y  kin thc v th qu kh n, gip cc bn d dng ghi nh nhanh chng  vn dng trong giao tip hoc t im ti a khi lm cc bi kim tra.'),(10,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p><h2>1. Cu trc</h2></p><p>Sau y l mt s cu trc lin quan n th qu kh tip din:</p><p></p><p>(+) Khng nh: S + was/were + V-ing +O</p><p>(-) Ph nh: S + wasn\'t/weren\'t + V-ing + O</p><p>(?) Hi  Wh - question:  Wh - question + was/were + S + V-ing?</p><p>(?) Hi Yes/no question: Was/Were + S + Ving...? -> Yes/No, S + was/were (not)</p><p>Gii thch k hiu: Xem chi tit</p><p></p><p><b>Lu :</b></p><p></p><p>Tobe \'was\' i vi cc ch ng s t nh: he, she, it, tn ring...</p><p>Tobe \'were\' i vi cc ch ng s nhiu nh: they, we, you...</p><p>c bit: Ch ng I i vi tobe \'was\'</p><p><h2>2. Cch dng</h2></p><p>Th qu kh tip din m t mt hnh ng ang din tin ti mt thi im c th trong qu kh</p><p>Chng ta thng s dng th qu kh tip din vi chc nng ny nu c s xut hin ca: When, all day, all the morning, at this time + khong thi gian,</p><p></p><p>V d: When I left home, my mother was cleaning my house</p><p></p><p> Hnh ng ang din tin lin tc trong mt khong thi gian nhm nhn mnh tnh lin tc ca n</p><p>V d: I was singing all day yesterday (Ti  ht lin tc trong ngy hm qua)</p><p></p><p>Mt hnh ng ang din ra trong qu kh th c hnh ng khc xen vo</p><p>Hnh ng ang din ra th dng th qu kh tip din, hnh ng xen vo th dng th qu kh n</p><p>V d: I was walking in the park when I suddenly fell over (Ti ang i b trong cng vin th bt ng vp ng)</p><p></p><p>Hai hnh ng xy ra ng thi trong qu kh</p><p>Chia c hai hnh ng  th qu kh tip din</p><p>V d: While I was cooking, my father was having shower (Trong khi ti nu n th b ti ang tm)</p><p></p><p>Hnh ng lp i lp li trong qu kh v lm phin n ngi khc</p><p>V d: When she worked here, she was always making noise (Khi c ta cn lm vic  y, c ta thng xuyn lm n)</p><p><h2>3. Du hiu nhn bit</h2></p><p>Ngoi vic da vo cch dng ca th Qu kh tip din, ng cnh ca cu th cc bn cng hy cn nhc s dng th Qu kh tip din khi c xut hin cc t nh:</p><p></p><p> While (trong khi)</p><p>When (khi)</p><p>At that time (vo thi im );</p><p>V d: At that time, I was looking for Forever book on the bookstore near my house</p><p>(Vo thi im , ti ang tm cun sch Forever  hiu sch gn nh)</p><p></p><p><h2>4. Bi tp vn dng</h2></p><p><b>Bi tp 1: Chia ng t  th qu kh tip din</b></p><p></p><p>I ___________________down the street when it begin to rain (go)</p><p>At this time last year, I ___________________an English course (attend)</p><p>Jim ________________ under the tree when he heard an explosion (stand)</p><p>The boy fell and hurt himself while he _________________ a bicycle (ride)</p><p>When we met them last year, they______________ in Santiago (live)</p><p>The tourist lost his camera while he________________ around the city (walk)</p><p>The lorry _______________ very fast when it hit our car (go)</p><p>While I ____________________in my room, my roommate ___________________ a party in the other room (study/ have)</p><p>Mary and I___________________ the house when the telephone rang (just leave)</p><p>We __________________ in the caf when they saw us (sit)</p><p><b>Bi tp 2: Chia ng t trong ngoc </b></p><p></p><p>     1. At this time last year, they (build) this house.</p><p></p><p>     2. I (drive) my car very fast when you called me.</p><p></p><p>     3. I (chat) with my friends while my teacher (teach) the lesson yesterday.</p><p></p><p>     4. My father (watch) TV when I got home.</p><p></p><p>     5. At this time yesterday, I (prepare) for my son\'s birthday party.</p><p></p><p>     6. What you (do) at 8 pm yesterday?</p><p></p><p>     7. Where you (go) when I saw you last weekend?</p><p></p><p>     8. They (not go) to school when I met them yesterday.</p><p></p><p>     9. My mother (not do) the housework when my father came home.</p><p></p><p>    10. My sister (read) books while my brother (play) football yesterday afternoon.</p>','qua-khu-tiep-dien.jpg','Past-continuous.png','Th qu kh tip din Past continuous','Bi vit s cung cp cho cc bn ton b kin thc lin quan n th qu kh tip din. Vi cch trnh by ngn gn d hiu, cc bn c th nh mt cch d dng  lm tt cc bi kim tra cng nh vt qua cc k thi t im cao.'),(11,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p><h2>1. Cu trc</h2></p><p>Di y l mt s cu trc ca th qu kh hon thnh:</p><p></p><p>(+) Khng nh: S + had + V-P2</p><p>(-) Ph nh: S + hadn\'t (had not) + V-P2</p><p>(?) Cu hi: Had + S + V-P2? -> Yes/No, S + had/hadn\'t</p><p>Gii thch k hiu: Xem chi tit</p><p></p><p><b>Lu : </b></p>  <p></p><p>V-P2 l ng t qu kh phn t 2. Nu l ng t bt quy tc th  ct 3 trong bng ng t bt quy tc. Nu l ng t c quy tc th thm -ed</p><p>Phn bit tr ng t  qu kh hon thnh \'had\' # ng t qu kh ca ng t thng have -> VP2: had (c)</p><p><h2>2. Cch dng</h2></p><p>Chng ta s s dng th qu kh hon thnh trong cc trng hp sau:</p><p></p><p>Khi c mt hnh ng xy ra v hon thnh trc mt hnh ng khc trong qu kh</p><p> Trong cu thng c 2 v, hnh ng no xy ra trc th dng qu kh hon thnh, hnh ng no xy ra sau th dng qu kh n</p><p> V d: He had gone to school before Sarah came</p><p></p><p>Hnh ng xy ra mt khong thi gian trong qu kh, trc mt mc thi gian khc</p><p>V d: I had lived abroad for three years when I received the letter from my best friend. (Ti  sng  nc ngoi c hai nm trc khi nhn c th t bn thn)</p><p></p><p> Hnh ng xy ra nh l iu kin tin quyt cho hnh ng khc</p><p>V d: My younger brother had prepared for the exams and was ready to do well. (Em trai ti  chun b k cng cho bi kim tra v sn sng  lm tt)</p><p></p><p><b>Lu : </b> So snh th Qu Kh Hon Thnh v th Qu Kh n</p><p></p><p></p><p> </p><p>Mt s bn ang cm thy kh khn khi phn bit th qu kh hon thnh v th qu kh n v c hai th ny u xy ra v kt thc trong qu kh, nhng hy nhn v d sau y, n s gip bn phn bit c hai th ny:</p><p>V d 1: </p><p></p><p>Was Hoa at the party when you arrived? (Hoa c  bui tic khi bn ti khng?)</p><p>No, he had already gone home. (Khng, anh y  v nh ri)</p><p></p><p>V d 2:</p><p>Was Tom there when you arrived? (Lc bn n Tom cn   khng?)</p><p>Yes, but he went home soon afterward. (C, nhng m ngay sau  anh ta v nh)</p><p></p><p><h2>3. Du hiu nhn bit</h2></p><p>Th qu kh hon thnh c s dng khi xut hin cc du hiu sau:</p><p></p><p>Chng ta thng s dng th qu kh hon thnh khi trong cu c cc t ni nh: before, after, just, when, as soon as, by the time, until, by the end of + time in the past </p><p>Cn li ph thuc vo cch dng ca th qu kh hon thnh  nu  trn, th mi nhn bit c.</p><p><h2>4. Bi tp vn dng</h2></p><p><b>Bi tp 1: Chia ng t ph hp</b></p><p></p><p>1. They (go) ..home after they (finish)  their work.</p><p></p><p>2. She said that she (already, see) . Dr. Rice.</p><p></p><p></p><p> </p><p>3. After taking a bath, he (go) .. to bed.</p><p></p><p>4. He told me he (not/eat)  such kind of food before.</p><p></p><p>5. When he came to the stadium, the match (already/ begin) .</p><p></p><p>6. Before she (watch) .. TV, she (do). homework.</p><p></p><p>7. What (be) .. he when he (be) . young?</p><p></p><p>8. After they (go) , I (sit) .. down and (rest) </p><p></p><p>9. Yesterday, John (go) .. to the store before he (go)  home.</p><p></p><p>10. She (win) . the gold medal in 1986.</p><p></p><p><b>Bi tp 2: Vit li cu sao cho ngha khng i, s dng t gi  cho sn. </b></p><p></p><p>1. David had gone home before we arrived.</p><p></p><p>-> After .</p><p></p><p>2. We had lunch then we took a look around the shops.</p><p></p><p>-> Before </p><p></p><p>3. The light had gone out before we got out of the office.</p><p></p><p>->When.</p><p></p><p>4. After she had explained everything clearly, we started our work.</p><p></p><p>-> By the time .</p><p></p><p>5. My father had watered all the plants in the garden by the time my mother came home.</p><p></p><p>-> Before .</p>','Th-qu-kh-hon-thnh-trong-ting-Anh.jpg','images.png','Th qu kh hon thnh Past perfect','Qu kh hon thnh l mt th kh v d nhm ln nht trong tt c cc th. Bi vit ny s gip cc bn d dng nh c cch dng, cu trc, cc du hiu nhn bit ca n.  vn dng vo lm bi tp, lm bi kim tra t im ti a.'),(12,NULL,NULL,'2022-04-20 15:37:45.235000','admin','<p><h2>1. Cu trc</h2></p><p>Sau y l mt s cu trc dng trong th tng lai n cn ghi nh:</p><p></p><p>(+) Khng nh: S + will + V nguyn th</p><p>(-) Ph nh: S + will not (won\'t) + V nguyn th</p><p>(?) Hi: Will + S + V nguyn th? -> Yes/No, S + will/ won\'t</p><p>Gii thch k hiu: Xem thm</p><p></p><p><b>Lu : </b></p>  <p></p><p>will not = won\'t</p><p>I will = I\'ll, You will = You\'ll, He will = He\'ll, She will = She\'ll, They will= they\'ll, we will = we\'ll...</p><p><h2>2. Cch dng</h2></p><p>Trong nhng trng hp sau, chng ta s chia  th hin ti n:</p><p></p><p>Din t mt quyt nh, mt  nh nht thi ny ra ngay ti thi im ni.</p><p>V d: Are you going to the park now? - I will go with you. (By gi bn ang ti cng vin ? T s i vi bn.)</p><p></p><p>(Ta thy quyt nh i ti cng vin c quyt nh ti thi im ni khi ch ng I gp ngi bn)</p><p></p><p>Din t mt d on khng c cn c. </p><p>V d: I think she will come to the party. (Ti ngh rng c y s ti ba tic.)</p><p></p><p>(D on rng c y s ti ba tic khng h c cn c no c)</p><p></p><p>Din t mt li ha hay li yu cu,  ngh.</p><p>V d: I promise that I will tell you the truth. (Ti ha l ti s ni vi bn s tht.)</p><p></p><p>S dng trong cu iu kin loi mt, din t mt gi nh c th xy ra  hin ti v tng lai.</p><p>V d: If she comes, I will go with her. (Nu c y n, ti s i vi c y.)</p><p></p><p>(Ta thy vic c y n hon ton c th xy ra nn ta s dng cu iu kin loi I  din t v mnh  chnh ta s dng th tng lai n.)</p><p></p><p><h2>3. Du hiu nhn bit</h2></p><p></p><p>Cc bn s dng th tng lai n khi xut hin cc du hiu sau:</p><p></p><p>C cc trng t ch thi gian trong tng lai:</p><p>in + thi gian: trong  na (in 2 minutes: trong 2 pht na)</p><p>tomorrow: ngy mai</p><p>Next day: ngy hm ti</p><p>Next week/ next month/ next year: Tun ti/ thng ti/ nm ti</p><p>C nhng ng t ch quan im nh:</p><p>think/ believe/ suppose/ : ngh/ tin/ cho l</p><p>perhaps: c l</p><p>probably: c l</p><p><h2>4. Bi tp vn dng</h2></p><p><b>Bi tp 1: Chia ng t trong ngoc</b></p><p></p><p>1. They (do) it for you tomorrow.</p><p></p><p>2. My father (call) you in 5 minutes.</p><p></p><p>3. We believe that she (recover) from her illness soon.</p><p></p><p>4.  I promise I (return) school on time.</p><p></p><p><b>Bi tp 2: Dng t gi  vit thnh cu hon chnh. </b></p><p></p><p>1. She/ hope/ that/ Mary/ come/ party/ tonight.</p><p></p><p>2. I/ finish/ my report/ 2 days.</p><p></p><p>3. If/ you/ not/ st