rmont Hotel that time.</p><p></p><p>A.will stay</p><p></p><p>B.will be staying</p><p></p><p><b>Bi tp 3: Chia ng t trong ngoc ph hp</b></p><p></p><p>1. (you/wait)______ at the station when she arrives?</p><p></p><p>2. I (drink)_________ at the pub while you are taking your exam!</p><p></p><p></p><p> </p><p>3. (she/visit)________ her Grandmother again this week?</p><p></p><p>4. At 3PM I (watch)__________ that movie on channel four.</p><p></p><p>5. (they/attend)____________ your concert next Friday? It would be lovely to see them.</p>','bbc80e7915a0fc645e1dbaa4aec369e7.jpg','maxresdefault.jpg','Th tng lai tip din Future Progressive','Bi vit s cung cp cho cc bn y  nhng kin thc lin quan n th tng lai tip din. Chng ta c th d dng ghi nh  vn dng lm bi tp, t im cao trong cc k thi.'),(14,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p><h2>1. Cu trc</h2></p><p>(+) Khng nh: S + will + have + Vp2</p><p>(-) Ph nh: S + won\'t + have + Vp2</p><p>(?) Hi:  Will + S + have + Vp2? -> Yes/No, S + will/ won\'t.</p><p>Gii thch k hiu: Xem thm</p><p></p><p><b>Lu : </b></p><p></p><p>Phn bit \'have\'  trn # ng t \'have\' (c)</p><p>Vp2 l ng t qu kh bt quy tc  ct 3 trong bng ng t bt quy tc. Hoc l V-ed vi nhng ng t c quy tc.</p><p><h2>2. Cch dng</h2></p><p>Dng  din t mt hnh ng hay s vic hon thnh trc mt thi im trong tng lai.</p><p>V d: I will have finished my homework before 9 oclock this evening.</p><p></p><p>(Cho n trc 9h ti nay ti s hon thnh xong bi tp v nh ri.)</p><p></p><p>Dng  din t mt hnh ng hay s vic hon thnh trc mt hnh ng hay s vic khc trong tng lai:</p><p>Hnh ng, s vic hon thnh trc s chia th tng lai hon thnh.</p><p></p><p>Hnh ng, s vic xy ra sau s chia th hin ti n.</p><p></p><p></p><p> </p><p>V d: I will have made the meal ready before the time you come tomorrow. (Trc khi bn n vo ngy mai, ti  chun b ba n sn sng)</p><p></p><p><h2>3. Du hiu nhn bit</h2></p><p>Chng ta s dng th tng lai hon thnh khi trong cu xut hin cc cm t ch thi gian  tng lai sau:</p><p></p><p>by + thi gian trong tng lai</p><p>by the end of + thi 